results.title: CNC Machinist Programmer
results.description: Job Description CNC/ MANUAL MACHINIST Fonon Technologies, a leading manufacturer of industrial laser and marking systems, has an IMMEDIATE opening for a CNC Machinist Responsibilities Perform set-ups and operation of all conventional & CNC machine shop equipment, including lathes, milling machines, horizontal boring mills, to very close tolerances. Responsible for coordinating work load based on shop schedule. Requirements K nowledge of controls and programming a plus Strong mathematical skills…
